Package gui

Provides the classes necessary to create and play the game with graphical application
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandCenter
    Defines window where the game is being played, the player can see the crew status, commit actions, view spaceship status, and visit outpost
    DarkSlider
    Defines a custom slider for the setup screen
    FinalScreen
    Defines window showing the final score when the game has ended
    GameGUI
    Defines GUI Manager that handles which window to open/close next
    ModernTab
    Defines a smart looking tab that is implemented in the Command Center window
    SetupScreen
    Defines window that handles the initial setup of crew member, game length and spaceship
    ShoppingCart
    Defines the shopping cart of the player, keeps track of items and prices
    StrandeD
    Defines the first window that shows the title, start and load button
